  "body": "When geth is started with an logfile argument that points to a non-existing path geth crashes.\n\n```\n> ./geth --logfile /tmp/nhonafsd/geth.log console\nWelcome to the FRONTIER\npanic: error opening log file '/tmp/nhonafsd/geth.log': open /tmp/nhonafsd/geth.log: no such file or directory\n\ngoroutine 1 [running]:\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/logger.openLogFile(0xc2080f2a20, 0x13, 0xc2080f2a40, 0x16, 0x2)\n    /home/bas/Development/golang/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/logger/log.go:16 +0x22f\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/logger.New(0xc2080f2a20, 0x13, 0xc2080f2a40, 0x16, 0x3, 0x0, 0x0)\n    /home/bas/Development/golang/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/logger/log.go:26 +0x1c4\ngithub.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/eth.New(0xc2080352b0, 0x4, 0x0, 0x0)\n    /home/bas/Development/golang/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/eth/backend.go:153 +0x91\nmain.console(0xc20806ac40)\n    /home/bas/Development/golang/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/cmd/geth/main.go:274 +0x6d\ngithub.com/codegangsta/cli.Command.Run(0xbbedb0, 0x7, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0, 0xcab390, 0x30, 0xe2bb30, ...)\n    /home/bas/Development/golang/src/github.com/codegangsta/cli/command.go:118 +0x104b\ngithub.com/codegangsta/cli.(*App).Run(0xc2080fe000, 0xc20800a000, 0x4, 0x4, 0x0, 0x0)\n    /home/bas/Development/golang/src/github.com/codegangsta/cli/app.go:178 +0xeaa\nmain.main()\n    /home/bas/Development/golang/src/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/cmd/geth/main.go:253 +0xb6\n```\n",
